  "analyst_note": "CVE-2025-31324 (SAP Note 3084487): Unauthenticated file upload via SAP NetWeaver Visual Composer /developmentserver/metadatauploader endpoint, allowing RCE. CVSS 10.0. If the /developmentserver/ path returns anything other than 404, the endpoint is exposed. This was a zero-day exploited in targeted attacks against large enterprises in 2025. Apply SAP Note 3084487 immediately. Also disable the /developmentserver/ component if not needed.",
